reviewText: I've enjoyed this very much.  The actors are great.  While I have an issue with a lot of the endings in Korean dramas, this ending is perfect.  Won't tell you.  Don't want to spoil it.  I know you will enjoy this.  Subtitles could use a good bit of improvement, especially toward the end, but it won't ruin anything for you.  Very nice Korean drama.  I recommend it.
